summary: A little human looking preset i made.
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][center][b]Description and installation instructions.

[/b]Hello! This is my first upload worthy face preset for racemenu of a female bosmer. It works well with other humanoid races aswell, but may require a little tweaking.

Simply, place the content of the arhve in your Skyrim/Data folder.
